1. DEFINITIONS
================================================================================

"Software" means source code, documentation, configuration, and other
materials in this repository, except Branding.

"Branding" means the names "Dev Center", "the-dev-center", "The Dev Center",
and any variant that suggests official or endorsed origin; all logos, icons,
splash screens, and visual identity; and any trade dress that would cause
confusion with the official Dev Center product. Branding is NOT licensed under
this document. Use of Branding requires separate written permission from the
copyright holder.

"Prohibited Distribution" means any distribution of the Software (or a
derivative) that:

  (a) is a frivolous or duplicate listing in an app store, marketplace, or
      similar distribution channel that adds no substantial value (e.g., a
      near-identical copy with no meaningful improvement or differentiation);

  (b) is malicious (e.g., contains malware, steals data, or harms users); or

  (c) is cognitively or commercially abusive, including but not limited to:
      stuffing the product with ads, dark patterns, or monetization that
      exploits users or the reputation of this project without adding
      commensurate value.

